用來實際地解決佢哋嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我當香港社會白養咗50個垃圾社工，炒哂＝一年慳1.5千萬，可以直接派畀有嚴重困難人士</blockquote><br />\n其實你知唔知社工做乜？兒童冇人照顧時帶佢去無良局，入院前要帶佢去body check，有晒法庭order，如果唔係無良局唔收。之後安排寄養服務，但唔係一勞永逸，因為冇可能永遠骨肉分離，所要定期要寫檢討報告。寄養家庭都要人督導，咪又係社工。只不過個名改得柒，乜撚都叫社工。其實跟職位叫，就唔會誤會，例如叫兒童保護及照顧安排主任，兒童之家經理，唔好叫乜撚社工。"},{"pid":"3ea01cc03facf3b1118d89338d662c6af34731a4","tid":126084,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T12:32:32.000Z","msg":"太窮就唔好生啦"},{"pid":"2cc37a78b1f1c8f609736bbae212d0d5136126d4","tid":126084,"uid":19505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T12:34:18.000Z","msg":"我尋晚得豉油撈飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a67717e810db1a6c8f54f82e708cb38e720c99","tid":126084,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T13:27:17.000Z","msg":"阿女結婚未"},{"pid":"2042fa0ac7ab7dc9d1473cbd883a85c533e12474","tid":126084,"uid":71725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T13:35:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2cbeaabcb29b012d1346a486121c647326d34f7b","tid":126084,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T13:41:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>紅衫魚滾菜湯<br />\n鼓油皇雞翼<br />\n咖哩魚蛋<br />\n<br />\n白飯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n轉做日文： <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n糸撚鯛野菜スープ<br />\nしょう油手羽先<br />\nカレー魚肉団子<br />\n<br />